==Daily==
===Searching for signal...===
{{Messages|text=
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Searching for signal...
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Unstable Signal
:'''Castorice:''' {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mr.}} (Trailblazer), if you are receiving this message, then you must have already departed the nether realm
:'''Castorice:''' I now feel that our farewell was far too rushed
:'''Castorice:''' It was only after you left that I remembered I still had something to tell you
:'''Castorice:''' I crocheted a little doll of you, (Trailblazer), but I didn't manage to finish stuffing it with milk cotton before I left
:'''Castorice:''' I also tried to recreate the Express as a cloth pendant based on your description
:'''Castorice:''' I tucked it inside a photo album. When decorated with dried flowers, it looked truly one of a kind
:'''Castorice:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 22 Castorice 01.png|80px]]
:'''Castorice:''' I had hoped that... when you reach the end of the Flame-Chase and stand witness to the birth of a new world, these items might bring you a trace of warmth
:'''Castorice:''' But in the end, I didn't even manage to give them to you in time
:'''Castorice:''' To ensure the new world's warmth, I will forever remain within this sea of flowers to watch over lost souls.
:'''Castorice:''' And if fate allows us to meet again, remember our promise
:{Choice} Deal
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Deal
:{Choice} When will we meet again?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' When will we meet again?
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Message failed to send.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} The user you're trying to reach is currently out of the service area. Please try again later.
}}
