==={{MC|m=Mr.|f=Miss}} (Trailblazer), long time no see~===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Castorice:''' {{MC|m=Mr.|f=Miss}} (Trailblazer), long time no see~
:'''Castorice:''' It feels so good to bask in the sunlight once again
:'''Castorice:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 21 Mem 02.png|80px]]
:{Choice} Finally, we meet again!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Finally, we meet again!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 02.png|80px]]
:{Choice} Long time no see, Castorice
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Long time no see, Castorice
:{Choice} Is that really you?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Is that really you?
::'''Castorice:''' Mm-hmm.
:'''Castorice:''' Even now, it still feels like a dream
:'''Castorice:''' Thanks to you and everyone else's efforts, things are finally different this time
:'''Castorice:''' [[File:Message Castorice 51.png|256px]]
:'''Castorice:''' Look, I adopted two stray little chimeras
:'''Castorice:''' They're warm and soft, perfect for cuddling up with when you're trying to sleep
:'''Castorice:''' It feels completely different from a chimera doll
:{Choice} Let me touch them!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Let me touch them!
::'''Castorice:''' Be my guest~
:{Choice} Dreams do come true!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Your dream has finally come true!
:'''Castorice:''' Though I wonder what names I should give them...
:'''Castorice:''' What are your thoughts on this?
:{Choice} Cas-cake, Cas-fly
::'''(Trailblazer):''' One is called Cas-cake, the other Cas-fly
::'''Castorice:''' Perfect, one is composed while the other is lively
::'''Castorice:''' It suits them perfectly!
:{Choice} Sweet talk or trash talk
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sweet talk or trash talk
::'''Castorice:''' I'll prefer... sweet talk
::'''Castorice:''' Oh, do you mean to use those as two separate names?
::'''Castorice:''' Maybe that's a bit too straightforward... hmm, let me think about it
:{Choice} I'm also terrible at coming up with names
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Actually, I'm also terrible at coming up with names
::'''Castorice:''' Hmm, let me think
:'''Castorice:''' The wind's picking up outside. Time to take them out for a walk.
:'''Castorice:''' @#$%...!**...&*
:'''Castorice:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 22 Castorice 03.png|80px]]
:'''Castorice:''' It was an accidental touch. They seem a bit too excited
:'''Castorice:''' Would you like to join us, if you have the time?
:'''Castorice:''' Then, I can give you that photo album I haven't had the chance to give you yet~
}}
