===Pardon me, {{MC|m=Mr.|f=Miss}} (Trailblazer)===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Castorice:''' Pardon me, {{MC|m=Mr.|f=Miss}} (Trailblazer)
:'''Castorice:''' Do you still recall the two little chimeras I adopted? I found out they love falling asleep to fairy tales
:'''Castorice:''' I've been thinking about exploring some new directions lately, so I'm planning to try writing
:{Choice} Castorice's new series!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' So what kind of new story do we have this time?
:{Choice} I want to be the protagonist
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Do I have a part in this?
::'''Castorice:''' Shouldn't be a problem
:'''Castorice:''' Actually, I was just about to ask for your opinion. Here's what I have in mind:
:'''Castorice:''' The protagonist accidentally enters a small town inhabited by cats and mice, singing crows, pink piglets, and a cooperative ant family
:'''Castorice:''' They're quite sociable, love playing with the protagonist, and really enjoy listening to stories
:'''Castorice:''' No, they love those stories very, very much...
:'''Castorice:''' When the fairy tale town enters deep night and everything quiets down... the little animals just can't fall asleep...
:'''Castorice:''' "It can't be quiet here," "It can't be quiet here," they said...
:'''Castorice:''' And so, they came to the protagonist's bedside
:'''Castorice:''' And just like that
:'''Castorice:''' ●_●
:'''Castorice:''' ◕_◕
:'''Castorice:''' ◐‿◑
:'''Castorice:''' They stare at you
:{Choice} That's terrifying!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Is this what you call a "fairy tale"? That's terrifying!
::'''Castorice:''' Ah, is it really terrifying?
::'''Castorice:''' To be honest, as I was writing, I realized this topic might be better suited for a horror novel
:{Choice} That's so cute!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Gotta admit, it's pretty cute
::'''Castorice:''' To be honest, as I was writing, I realized this topic might be better suited for a horror novel
::'''Castorice:''' But judging from your reaction, I'm afraid the horror elements aren't quite enough
:{Choice} Where is that quiet place?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' So where is that quiet place?
::'''Castorice:''' As expected, your focus is always so... unique
::'''Castorice:''' To be honest, as I was writing, I realized this topic might be better suited for a horror novel
:'''Castorice:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 22 Castorice 04.png|80px]]
:'''Castorice:''' I'm not that well-versed in horror novels, so to better immerse myself, I looked up some reference books, like ''20 Unsolved Mysteries'' and ''The Many Causes of Disappearances''...
:'''Castorice:''' I just finished reading ''Eat Well'' today and got some pretty good ideas from it
:'''Castorice:''' I'll come back to discuss with you once I make some progress
:'''Castorice:''' Don't worry, the little chimeras will pester me daily for updates. They just can't live without stories!
:'''Castorice:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 22 Castorice 01.png|80px]]
}}
